\begin_inset Formula $T$
\end_inset

 the temperature.
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\overline{\varepsilon} & \approx\Delta\varepsilon\approx k_{B}T\\
\Rightarrow\qquad\frac{\Delta\varepsilon}{\overline{\varepsilon}} & \approx1
\end{align*}

