 The average momentum 
\begin_inset Formula $\overline{p_{r}}$
\end_inset

 per particle is:
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\overline{p_{r}} & =\frac{\pi\hbar}{L}\overline{n_{r}}
\end{align*}

\end_inset

For 
\begin_inset Formula $\overline{n_{r}}\gg1$
\end_inset

, i.e.
 
\begin_inset Formula $\overline{p_{r}}\gg\frac{\pi\hbar}{L}$
\end_inset

