\end_inset

Finally, 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand eqref
reference "eq:gibbs_enthalpy"

\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand eqref
reference "eq:G_Nmu"

\end_inset

