Note
\emph default
: Equation 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand eqref
reference "eq:caloricState"

\end_inset

 is a particular realization of the 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

equipartition theorem
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

, which states:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Quote
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

Each variable occurring 
\emph on
quadratically
\emph default
 in the Hamiltonian yields a contribution of 
