\hat{a}_{k} & =\int_{0}^{L}\dd x\left\langle k|x\right\rangle \hat{a}\left(x\right)=\frac{1}{\sqrt{L}}\int_{0}^{L}\dd xe^{-\ii kx}\hat{a}\left(x\right)
