\end{align*}

\end_inset

Hence we get:
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align}
\fbox{\ensuremath{{\displaystyle M\omega^{2}\vec{\epsilon}=\mat D\left(\vec{k}\right)\vec{\epsilon}}}}
\end{align}

\end_inset

Because 
\begin_inset Formula $\mat D\left(\vec{k}\right)$
\end_inset

