\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\left[\hat{b}_{\vec{k}_{1},\lambda_{1}},\hat{b}_{\vec{k}_{2},\lambda_{2}}\right] & =\delta_{\vec{k}_{1},\vec{k}_{2}}\delta_{\lambda_{1}\lambda_{2}}
\end{align*}

\end_inset

To find the Hamiltonian describing the lattice dynamics, we go back to 
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{H}_{\text{ion}}$
\end_inset

